 * to share the same IP address. This will cause the rate limiter to incorrectly
 * throttle unrelated users as if they were a single client.
 *
 * Always configure trust proxy BEFORE mounting this middleware.
 * ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
 *
 * @module rate-limiter
 */

